@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### GET /announcements — без параметрів
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements

###

### GET /announcements — з параметром search
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements?search=ноутбук

###

### GET /announcements — з параметрами sort та page
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements?sort=oldest&page=1

###

### GET /announcements/:id — існуючий id
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements/1

###

### GET /announcements/:id — неіснуючий id
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements/99999

###

### POST /announcements — валідні дані
POST {{baseUrl}}/announcements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Продам ноутбук Dell XPS",
  "description": "Відмінний стан, 16GB RAM, SSD 512GB",
  "price": 25000,
  "category": "sale",
  "contactInfo": "0991234567"
}

###

### POST /announcements — невалідні дані (показує роботу валідації)
POST {{baseUrl}}/announcements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "ab",
  "price": -100
}

###

### PATCH /announcements/:id — часткове оновлення
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/announcements/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 22000
}

###

### PATCH /announcements/:id — неіснуючий id
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/announcements/99999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 100
}

###

### DELETE /announcements/:id
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/announcements/1

###

### DELETE /announcements/:id — неіснуючий id
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/announcements/99999
